{"tid":1208064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7名前港府官員發公開信　促請林鄭撤回修例","createTime":"2019-06-12T08:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T08:53:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8fcaef31c2705eb628ba2dc02e0b3c2bd4829d87","tid":1208064,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:46:58.000Z","msg":"7名港府前局長、副局長和政治助理今日向特首林鄭月娥發公開信，要求及早撤回《逃犯條例》修訂草案。是次去信的包括前勞工及福利局長蕭偉強、前運輸及房屋局副局長邱誠武、前政治助理陳志遠、莫宜端、葉根銓、蔡少棉、羅永聰，他們指近日社會和立法會對法案有極度爭議，不少理性和務實建議未及充分討論和回應，而且罕有地引起大量市民以遊行表達關注，疑慮有待釋除，要求林鄭為創造空間讓社會作理性交流和討論，及早撤回方案。<br />\n<br />\n他們促請林鄭聆聽各方意見，尤其是直接涉及法律專業，促進和諧互信，繼續尋求中央信任和廣大市民支持。7人同時呼籲，各方表達意見和行動時，本著仁愛、尊重、和平、理性及克制的大原則。<br />\n<br />\n7人之中，蕭偉強和邱誠武與林鄭一樣，都是上屆政府的官員，其中蕭偉強在1978年加入政府任職行政主任，曾經是現任政務司司長張建宗在勞福局的直屬下屬，分別出任局長和副局長。"},{"pid":"5fa2d6ae697abae725b91eca125c65f18baca26a","tid":1208064,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:48:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c4c9cad29d822bb26e7e7ec3508b7f6e6bad3a","tid":1208064,"uid":47558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:48:06.000Z","msg":"希望而家有 d 大袋落一落示威區，唔係真係血流成河"},{"pid":"f6b162a08614cac46da852ff99d38a32471a932f","tid":1208064,"uid":185215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:50:07.000Z","msg":"有冇source"},{"pid":"7662f36b579e3f37c6649b1c07314015cbe9f4b1","tid":1208064,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:51:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190612/59707221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190612%2F59707221&d=LMVY6Z7nIekaHefcscWgVYtKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=00cd71cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190612%2F59707221&h=4a99ec80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190612/59707221</a>"},{"pid":"b82e3f0f699b165bed0f57dfad86539c569cbb11","tid":1208064,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}